latestPosts.caption:
Besties, this weekend was truly one for the books! I experienced SO MANY FIRSTS — my first time EVER at @txfashionweek and my very first RUNWAY SHOW! 🫶 I’m beyond BLESSED to have shared this unforgettable moment with the amazing team at @texasfashionindustry 📸

As a fashion girly, being able to experience this moment was literally tears of joy! , from learning more about the fashion scene in Texas @texasfashionindustry at the Conference, to connecting with new amazing people, and being surrounded with individuals who also have the same passion for fashion! 👗

Every designer left me speechless. The creativity, the attention to detail, the fabrics, the textures, y mucho más — I honestly couldn’t pick a favorite because they were ALL iconic. 🖤

Besties if you missed this past @txfashionweek no worries they will be coming back in FALL stay tuned for that, this is an experience YOU need to have! 

MILLIONS of thank you to @texasfashionindustry for having me this past weekend — this is only the beginning 💫🤍 

.
.
.

Besties! Are you looking to do something fun and different this summer? Then come with me to a Crêpe Culinary Class at the @sabotgarden 🌺 

Chef Louise Bly walked us through each step of making the perfect crêpe — yes, even the iconic pan flip! 🥞 She explained everything so clearly and made it super easy, even for a first-timer like me 👩‍🍳

Whether you’re planning a mom-and-daughter date, a girls’ night out, a solo adventure, or just want to try something new, this class is a must! Highly recommend checking out @sabotgarden for their next one ✨
.

Besties! @tasteofthenorthside is definitely a can’t miss Fiesta event 🪅✨🩷 

It was my FIRST TIME experiencing this event and I have to say it was a good one, restaurants from San Antonio & other local businesses were showcasing their delicious food and drinks! And definitely not forgetting live entertainment ✨

Every ticket gives back to the @brightoncentersa LARGEST non - profit foundation in San Antonio serving the children that have disabilities and delays here in San Antonio! 

So if you missed out on @tasteofthenorthside this year STAY TUNED FOR NEXT YEAR 🎉 

Thank you so much for having me! 🪅✨🤍

latestPosts.caption:
Besties! Are you looking to dine in downtown San Antonio? Then welcome to @beaustinydiner located in Southtown 🩵✨🍽️

@beaustinydiner offers a range of varieties weather your craving breakfast, lunch, dinner or just want to share a snack with your besties, they have you covered! 

We had their Honeybun, Yogurt Parfait for breakfast option , then for shareable options we had their loaded nachos & onion rings for the main course it was a must to try their Green Enchiladas and Spicy Chicken Sandwich 🍽️ 

So if your near the downtown area or looking for something to eat after / before fiesta activities make sure to stop by 🥂 

.
.
